{"id": 2760, "genre": 1001, "title": "【好奇心x戴森】办公室的哪个瞬间会让你“喘不过气”？", "description": "人在职场总有那么些事儿能让人在某个瞬间无法呼吸接近崩溃。", "record_count": 11714, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190126213456Corin8GtJUyXY4sx.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 3, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-01-27T03:00:38Z", "options": [{"id": 324865, "content": "开会超过一小时", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1143922}, {"id": 324866, "content": "领导心情不好的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1437481}, {"id": 324867, "content": "大冬天的进来一个全身汗臭味的同事，该开窗吗？？？", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433801}, {"id": 324868, "content": "办公室的空调热到像是蒸桑拿", "image": null, "praise_count": 43, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1107203}, {"id": 324870, "content": "领导在办公室抽烟 且是日常 真的会很崩溃", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 918581}, {"id": 324871, "content": "公司一搬家全是物料，随便找个东西扬起漫天灰尘，分分钟要窒息", "image": null, "praise_count": 454, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 324872, "content": "无处不在的浓烈香水味……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1208858}, {"id": 324873, "content": "一起开会时有同事抽烟，令人崩溃", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1107227}, {"id": 324874, "content": "下了班，大楼空调停了，老板和男同事毫不掩饰的开始抽烟了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1223792}, {"id": 324875, "content": "加班", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1155928}, {"id": 325131, "content": "没有意义的加班统计数！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1430105}, {"id": 324876, "content": "最忍受不了的：浓浓的香水味～好像别人鼻子都是坏掉的一样", "image": null, "praise_count": 269, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1482927}, {"id": 324877, "content": "精致的同事每天更换桌上的插花，花粉过敏的我备受煎熬", "image": null, "praise_count": 462, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433852}, {"id": 324879, "content": "整个办公室都不敢大声说话的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 193, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433920}, {"id": 324880, "content": "密闭的空间里，有人堂而皇之地抽烟，还连续两根，使人抓狂", "image": null, "praise_count": 319, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1424920}, {"id": 324881, "content": "办公室有同事犯错了 气压低", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433873}, {"id": 325137, "content": "在公司吃螺蛳粉，啧啧啧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1488990}, {"id": 324882, "content": "有人在办公室吃螺蛳粉！丧尽天良", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433806}, {"id": 325138, "content": "领导布置完一个指向不明的任务后就走人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1570372}, {"id": 324883, "content": "老板发火的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1235379}, {"id": 324884, "content": "老板发货的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1235379}, {"id": 324885, "content": "男同事喷“迷人”的印度神香…", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433947}, {"id": 324886, "content": "同事口气很重的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 198, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433922}, {"id": 324887, "content": "居然有人会在办公室吃榴莲？真的不知道怎么想的", "image": null, "praise_count": 167, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433882}, {"id": 324888, "content": "奇怪食物的味道", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1378846}, {"id": 324889, "content": "夏天潮湿的味道", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433929}, {"id": 324890, "content": "隐隐约约的老鼠的味道", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433996}, {"id": 324891, "content": "实习生的香水熏死我呀", "image": null, "praise_count": 148, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1555110}, {"id": 324892, "content": " 精致的同事每天更换桌上的插花，花粉过敏的我备受煎熬", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1568666}, {"id": 324893, "content": "上班时间鸦雀无声，很压抑，跟上坟一样", "image": null, "praise_count": 322, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1432000}, {"id": 324894, "content": "没有Booking上大会议室，10个人的会议被安排在5人会议室，“人气”爆棚", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1557864}, {"id": 324895, "content": "因为在特殊单位做文职，几个大妈退休级别的天天在里面聊家常，天天夸自己家儿女亲戚，也就是别人家的孩子那种。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1482736}, {"id": 324896, "content": "和同事产生矛盾了就感觉喘不过气", "image": null, "praise_count": 338, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433847}, {"id": 324897, "content": "口臭！隔着一米说话都能闻到散发出强烈下水道臭味的IT男", "image": null, "praise_count": 604, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 879838}, {"id": 324898, "content": "做错事的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433983}, {"id": 324899, "content": "几个同事吃了带蒜味的菜的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433900}, {"id": 340004, "content": "桌面很大，但很挤", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1639260}, {"id": 324900, "content": "同事瘋狂甩臭臉的辦公室真的踹不過氣👋🏻", "image": null, "praise_count": 359, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433932}, {"id": 325668, "content": "背后有人走来走去", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 901471}, {"id": 324901, "content": "同事突然放了个屁 又好笑又不能说啥", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433805}, {"id": 324902, "content": "有同事开着窗 而外面都是柳絮", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1434017}, {"id": 324903, "content": "同事自以为是的好闻香水却让人掩鼻窒息", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433962}, {"id": 324904, "content": "办公室里都是粉尘", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433818}, {"id": 324905, "content": "大扫除时候空气里都是灰尘", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433911}, {"id": 324906, "content": "公司一搬家全是物料，随便找个东西扬起漫天灰尘，分分钟要窒息", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1568985}, {"id": 324907, "content": "男同事夏天时候身上都会汗臭味", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433849}, {"id": 324908, "content": "吃完鸡蛋跟我说话 我真是想给他嘴巴打歪", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1558080}, {"id": 324909, "content": "现在商务楼基本没有可以开的窗，热空调一开就干，加湿器也只能发挥局部效应", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1107407}, {"id": 324910, "content": "居然有人会在办公室脱鞋！重点是有脚臭味", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1434042}, {"id": 324911, "content": "同事买了超级香的好吃的，飘到我这里的时候……", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1568986}]}